FBIS4-60200 "drnes099_j_94028" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 22 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Wrapup of Reports on Clashes, Military Operations Wrapup of Reports on Clashes, Military Operations Radio Reports Scud Attack on Aden EA2205165394 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 22 May 94 EA2205165394 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Excerpt] This morning Scud missiles hit the city of Aden. One missile fell on the populated areas of Khawr Maksar killing whole families. Many citizens in the populated Sa'adah area were seriously wounded. Only two days ago, the city of Aden was subjected to similar barbaric attacks in that same area. Aden port, the oil refinery in al-Burayqah town, and the geothermal station at al-Hiswah were also effected. [passage omitted]
